==========================================================================================
FILE            IMPLEMENTATION FOCUS   
==========================================================================================
api.c           The standard API functions for libadam -and adam_data struct definition
cli.c           Command line - option parsing, pretty printing info, manipulating ADAM
ent.c           ENT framework code with some arrangement tweaks to work with the adam CLI
rng.c           Where the magic happens! All the necessary primitives for ADAM
support.c       Miscellaneous helpers and utility functions for CLI
test.c          Some tests and measurements of statistical quality, for the -e CLI option